OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780484573
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner
OL,4,CMohamed Al Fayed to meet PM
OL,6,FSurvivors of abuse by former Harrods
OL,7,Fowner Mohamed Al Fayed will meet with
OL,8,Fthe prime minister on Wednesday to
OL,9,Fpush for greater accountability for
OL,10,Fwhat they describe as "decades of
OL,11,Finstitutional rape and sexual abuse".
OL,13,FSurvivor groups said they hope the
OL,14,Fmeeting with Keir Starmer will be a
OL,15,F"landmark moment" for justice.
OL,17,FMore than 400 allegations of sexual
OL,18,Fmisconduct have been made against Al
OL,19,FFayed, dating back to 1977.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@dO]wD@AOUwD@QO]
