PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780484573
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner
OL,4,CMohamed Al Fayed to meet PM
OL,6,FLucy Duckworth, policy lead for the
OL,7,FSurvivors Trust, who will chair the
OL,8,Fmeeting, said it must be a "turning
OL,9,Fpoint" for survivors of sex abuse and
OL,10,Fcalled for policymakers to address
OL,11,F"the wider systemic failures that
OL,12,Fallowed abuse on this scale to occur
OL,13,Fand persist".
OL,15,FShe added: "Lasting change will depend
OL,16,Fon transparency, accountability, and a
OL,17,Fcommitment to strengthening
OL,18,Fsafeguarding across institutions."
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@FO]sD@AOUuD@LO]wD@LOUzD@bO]
