PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780484573
OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner
OL,4,CMohamed Al Fayed to meet PM
OL,6,FThe Survivors Trust says the meeting
OL,7,Fwith Starmer will mark the first time
OL,8,Fa prime minister has engaged directly
OL,9,Fwith survivors connected to a "single
OL,10,Finstitution", but stressed it should
OL,11,Fmark "the beginning of sustained
OL,12,Fengagement with the Government, rather
OL,13,Fthan an end point".
OL,15,FThe APPG is calling for a full
OL,16,Funderstanding of what it calls
OL,17,F"systemic failures" surrounding
OL,18,FHarrods and action to prevent further
OL,19,Fabuse.
OL,26,@qD@_OUrD@LO]sD@FOUuD@RO]yD@AOUyD@SO]
