OL,3,CSurvivors of abuse by Harrods owner
OL,4,CMohamed Al Fayed to meet PM
OL,6,FHarrods set up a redress scheme to
OL,7,Foffer compensation and counselling for
OL,8,Fthose affected and praised "the
OL,9,Fbravery of all survivors in coming
OL,10,Fforward".
